title: Conrad Weiser blanks Schuylkill Valley for key league win
text:
Large Text Conrad Weiser blanks Schuylkill Valley for key league win 
project. >>>rob vaughn: >> wendy davis: >>>troy hein:>>> the conrad weiser girls had a tremendous year last year, winning a lot of games in every sport it seemed. fall, winter, spring, the scouts were in the hunt. the field hockey team is continuing that run this year, the scouts have just one league loss this year and hoped to keep it that way today with a win over schuylkill valley...
